TITLE: Adding Middleware to Specific Routes in Loco-rs
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to add a middleware layer to a specific route in a Loco-rs application. It shows the configuration of routes for a 'notes' controller, applying a LogLayer middleware to the 'create' endpoint.
